QuestData.Title: Charged Moganite
QuestData.Description: We have been dispatching spies into the Kirin Tor base of operations on a daily basis. Some had orders to recover charged moganite from the enemy and bring it here.$b$bThey have not returned, and I can confirm they have left the Kirin Tor base.$b$bSearch the jungle between here and there and find any of the charged moganite that might have been lost in transit. Bring it to me and we will put it to good use.
QuestData.LogDescription: Recover a Charged Moganite and bring it to High Arcanist Savor.

Objectives.Objective: Charged Moganite returned to Dawnseeker Promontory
